window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Fight the tides of evil, build a team, and restore balance in the universe!</b></p> <p>Kelvin comes from an isolated community of fierce warriors known as the Xaros. They train rigorously to battle across the portal realms while earning levels, experience and loot. Through their conquests, they allow their society to operate in safety, often even sacrificing their mind, body, and spirit to protect the whole.</p> <p>On coming of age, Kelvin ventures away from home with his twin battle axes infused with magic. He's eager to slay foes and repay the investment sunk into his fancy gear â€” paid for through the blood and lives of his ancestors.</p> <p>On his first mission, he encounters a very rare dungeonling. Hanna is an elven princess turned vampire, nothing more than a tool of her master to punish her people. Together, they'll form a team who'll struggle vto right the great wrongs of the universe with blade, bow, and magic.</p> <p><b>Join Kelvin, Hanna, and a few extras in a growing team on an epic adventure fit for the ages.</b></p>"; 
